[...and to Ryan for chasing this storm.

The OIE designation of the strain as LPAI (Low pathogenic avian influenza) refers to its mild effect in poultry, not to its lethal effect in humans.

See hundreds of live pigeons for wholesale in the Shanghai market on 3 Apr 2013:
http://media.therecord.com/images/c6/5d/b566b3ff4eac953f204fca4423ee.jpg

Photo of culling in Shanghai market:
